# init()

**Initializer**

Creates an empty fetch operation.

## Declaration

```swift
init()
```

## Discussion

You must set [doc://com.apple.cloudkit/documentation/CloudKit/CKFetchWebAuthTokenOperation/apiToken] before you execute the operation or add it to a queue.

## Creating a Fetch Token Operation

- **init(apiToken:)**: Creates a fetch operation for the specified API token.
